subject: Boats and Boating
Volvo Ocean Race
lead_paragraph: The United States yacht Pirates of the Caribbean won the ninth and final leg of the Volvo Ocean Race on, but the Dutch entry ABN Amro One was the overall winner in the grueling around-the-world regatta.
